sections.heading: proceedings; not to delay distribution of other shares
sections.text: The proceedings in relation to the encumbrances shall not delay the distribution of the proceeds of other shares in respect to which no difficulties exist.SourceR.S.1867, Code ยง 827, p. 540;R.S.1913, ยง 8310;C.S.1922, ยง 9262;C.S.1929, ยง 20-2194;R
